Scheduling in linux
	1. Core scheduling (priority based preemptive) 
	2. policy plugin 
		-->General purpose scheduling  --to be used for the task which have the priority 0
			SCHED_OTHER(Default), SCHED_IDLE, SCHED_BATCH
		-->Real time scheduling        --to be used for the task which have the priority (1-99)
			SCHED_RR, SCHED_FIFO
		-->Deadline scheduling 
			SCED_DEADLINE

